casebody.data:
Darryl Scott HONOWITZ, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
LOTUS & OAK, LLC, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-0448 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. AUGUST 23, 2018 EMAS, FERNANDEZ and LUCK, JJ., concur.

ORDERED that appellee's motion to dismiss appeal is granted, and this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is hereby dismissed. See Cukierman v. Bankatlantic, 89 So. 3d 250 (Fla. 3d DCA 2012).
